Elm Developper Information

Directories:
	include/		ELM headers
	src/			ELM sources
	test/			Test programs
	tools/			Tool to work with ELM.

Bootstrap:
	cmake .
Under Windows:
	cmake . -G "MSYS Makefiles"

Auto-documentation:
	xdg-open autodoc/index.html

Re-generating the autodocumentation:
	cmake . -DAUTODOC=ON

Activating the test compilation:
	cmake . -DELM_TEST=ON

Testing:
	test/test			launch all automated tests
	test/test-thread	thread classes

Under Windows:
	move src/libelm.dll to test/


